Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.73,0:01:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我保證…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.81,0:01:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,愛妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.37,0:02:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,砂糖姊姊還沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.00,0:02:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道出了什麼事…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.96,0:02:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,要是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.17,0:02:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,她不再回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,外頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,砂糖姊姊在外頭 對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:02:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但是砂糖姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:03:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我外頭很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.89,0:03:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟妳一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,砂糖姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,砂糖姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.27,0:03:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,砂糖姊姊 妳在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,妳在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,妳為什麼不回家？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我得消滅他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:04:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不！別離開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.07,0:04:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我得盡快…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,砂糖姊姊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 松坂小姐 抱歉把妳留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我剛才才聯絡到店長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我很好 別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.39,0:04:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,旭…旭…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,快來抓我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,喔！你醒了！感謝老天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧？ 你還不能動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,至少你骨頭沒斷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,總之 店長馬上就來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-我要回家 -什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:04:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我想醫院應該還開著…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜你住附近吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 原來如此！ 那我帶你回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我很擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-好嗎？ -沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉給你添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,還有抱歉弄髒你的沙發
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望他能回到家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.75,0:05:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我不該管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也回家吧 松坂小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.76,0:05:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我控制不了我的情緒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.95,0:06:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我在那裡消滅了那個東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但這是什麼感受？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不是第一次嚐到苦澀的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但這是完全不同的層次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,只記得會帶來苦澀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼感覺？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,憤怒？痛苦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,警告的訊號？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.12,0:06:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這跟我之前任何的感受都不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:06:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,苦澀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不 別再想了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我失控 我也會失去我跟小鹽的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我必須理解控制
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我想像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,小鹽跟那東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.23,0:07:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,彼此說著誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我的嘴感到苦澀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我愛的人跟別人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這是嫉妒嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,嫉妒！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高興！因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.15,0:08:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這情感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.69,0:08:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.53,0:08:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是來自我對小鹽的愛 對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我的第一個愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,回家嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,要跟我們一起玩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我愛的人在家等我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝 小鹽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我感覺重獲新生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我等不及要回家！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,回到我親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,幸福砂糖生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.41,0:09:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,妳好可愛 神戶鹽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.83,0:09:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,（尋找神戶鹽）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但怎麼回事 小鹽？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,妳被綁架了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？我覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這傳單也在公園裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我認為不重要 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.86,0:09:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我得確保那東西跟小鹽 絕對不會碰面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他妨礙我們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我得技術上消除他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.26,0:10:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,下次 我會忍住 不論有多苦澀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我只要小鹽知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我回家了 小鹽！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.25,0:10:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,小鹽？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,小鹽？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,小鹽？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,小鹽！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.13,0:10:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,她不在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,小鹽！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.62,0:11:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,（公園規定）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,旭…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 旭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.36,0:11:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我很堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-照顧鹽 -但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝會眷顧我們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧 我保證…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有天我會來接你們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.09,0:11:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,旭…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,妳在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你要被處罰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,如果惡魔存在這世上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我確定就是這個模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,她是否活著 是否安全
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,鹽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我得找到鹽！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,妳在哪裡 鹽！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.23,0:12:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好多人 我好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我從那邊走…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,砂糖姊姊 我好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.04,0:13:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,旋轉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,像是我頭被扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.59,0:13:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.97,0:13:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,妳是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,過來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我腳痛 又冷又痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我很寂寞 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.04,0:13:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.58,0:13:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,妳是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前來過這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.51,0:14:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但我覺得她一直牽著我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺好懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.62,0:14:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,再一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘記了什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.83,0:14:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,妳是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:15:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒想到會在這裡找到妳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.73,0:15:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,神戶鹽！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.28,0:15:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,3rd Life: 漫長單調的夜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這表示她是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛的小手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,手指頭 小孩子的溫度…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,可愛的小嘴唇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,純潔、無辜、大眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她好可愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.57,0:15:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 我一直想要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,她幫我做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:15:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:16:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,幫我個忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,求求妳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我要妳親吻我的傷口 讓它消失！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,消失吧 傷口！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,消失吧 傷口！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,消失吧 傷口！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,消失吧 傷口！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎麼知道我的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,神戶鹽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.82,0:16:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,神戶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.25,0:16:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我很髒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,自從那女人玩弄我的身體那天…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但是當妳觸碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:17:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我感覺自己被淨化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我感覺很開心 真的很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.11,0:17:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,來 來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你的頭髮顏色很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,來 來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.74,0:17:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,三星太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,太陽？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.29,0:17:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就是太陽哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.62,0:17:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,來 太陽哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哭會讓你難過 別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.22,0:17:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,她是天使
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,她是天使
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,她是來安慰我的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.31,0:17:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒弄錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.65,0:17:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我感受到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次見到妳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:18:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺妳是能夠淨化我的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,並沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,小鹽 我沒想到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我能夠遇見妳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝肯定是注意到我的努力了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我要妳再碰我！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.93,0:18:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,再碰我！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.97,0:18:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我淨化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.23,0:18:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,太陽哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.85,0:18:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我也對那個人做同樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我為什麼想不起來？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.45,0:18:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得我不該忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛 我好難過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.58,0:18:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不知什麼原因
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很難過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.26,0:19:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道砂糖姊姊知不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,妳說的是妳家人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.07,0:19:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,家人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,妳走失了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.36,0:19:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他們在找妳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,妳爸爸、媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,妳愛的人都會在妳身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.25,0:19:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,妳說得對 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那我把妳愛的人帶來這裡如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.22,0:19:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,妳就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,砂糖姊姊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 砂糖姊姊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,瞭解！太陽哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定也知道砂糖姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.24,0:20:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就麻煩你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那這之前 妳能夠待在我家嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.99,0:20:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 直到我找到她…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我要這女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.13,0:20:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,更進一步淨化我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,太陽哥 你還好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.14,0:20:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,為了這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.90,0:20:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,也許下次該我碰妳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.82,0:20:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我們可以做好多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.11,0:20:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我錯過這個機會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能再也見不到她了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.83,0:20:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 老天 原諒我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:21:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,再一下子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,只要再一下子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.27,0:21:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,老天 那有個金髮很搶眼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到你又回到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.49,0:21:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你是白癡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 原來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.15,0:21:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我們現在能夠還你 早先打攪我們的代價了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.81,0:21:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,小鹽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.36,0:22:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-他好大聲 -要帶他去廁所嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.15,0:22:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是 不能讓任何人看見我們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,又開始痛了 我的頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.79,0:22:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我看見紅色的東西？紅色…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.67,0:22:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.01,0:22:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛 我怕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.38,0:22:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.64,0:22:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,救命！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.49,0:24:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,自從我遇到小鹽 我就一直改變
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.66,0:24:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你看？我今晚也有新的情緒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.08,0:24:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,4th Life: 砂糖女孩沒發現
